{"tid":1809953,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[黨鐵] 不如將飛站班次常規化好唔好？","createTime":"2020-01-03T12:43:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-03T17:32:56.000Z","uid":123613,"like":4,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"f627aaf644cfb37973b3126cb1d0760292da8a44","tid":1809953,"uid":123613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T12:43:28.000Z","msg":"早排成日玩飛站，啲港豬可能已經習慣咗，係時候可以將飛站班次常規化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n繁忙時間有時閂好多次門先開車，整到條線delay晒，月台上嘅客可能上唔到車，為確保維持99.9%準時率，不如隨意飛啲少人用或者少人落車嘅站好唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n例如石硤尾 樂富 牛頭角 佐敦 長沙灣 天后 炮台山 西灣河 車公廟 錦上路 柯士甸 九龍呢堆站就係飛站首選<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 當然唔少得火炭 沙田 大埔呢啲有幾條路軌嘅站<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有返工時間嘅北角(去中環) 旺角(去中環) 油塘(去北角)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n放工時間嘅太子(去調景嶺) 金鐘(去荃灣同柴灣)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42bc67b27b882e40156655a7427b8cd0106d7137","tid":1809953,"uid":123613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T12:45:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c3765ac0d67e19c78aa7a35cce1d122deae3d7e","tid":1809953,"uid":1159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T12:46:12.000Z","msg":"哪有軌，你老母"},{"pid":"38cfce0d7e9726f80504a6b2479058ebfae21ddd","tid":1809953,"uid":123613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3c3765ac0d67e19c78aa7a35cce1d122deae3d7e","tid":1809953,"uid":1159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T12:46:12.000Z","msg":"哪有軌，你老母"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T12:48:51.000Z","msg":"繁忙時間本來係2分鐘一班，下一班突然間話要4分鐘先到，飛一個站都唔會追到前面班車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c451989f8fdeb2b9e8749af8b77a9e2ccaedf859","tid":1809953,"uid":120627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T12:49:51.000Z","msg":"好 批准<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"614b7bb94e53cf89e1f0ed3dbf212ffc01e87a4c","tid":1809953,"uid":164961,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T12:54:29.000Z","msg":"黨鐵不了"},{"pid":"bb2310df865e97f01560b4b07a1498606ca116cc","tid":1809953,"uid":11067,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T12:57:07.000Z","msg":"但係之前係飛晒啲多人落車嘅站喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"594aaabeedaad2a40e8e0e8e0efe5fb172ca70e2","tid":1809953,"uid":123613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"38cfce0d7e9726f80504a6b2479058ebfae21ddd","tid":1809953,"uid":123613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3c3765ac0d67e19c78aa7a35cce1d122deae3d7e","tid":1809953,"uid":1159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T12:46:12.000Z","msg":"哪有軌，你老母"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T12:48:51.000Z","msg":"繁忙時間本來係2分鐘一班，下一班突然間話要4分鐘先到，飛一個站都唔會追到前面班車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T13:01:00.000Z","msg":"例如有班車喺00分到九龍塘，04分到太子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁下班車delay咗，04分先到九龍塘，飛石硤尾個時間可以快1-2分鐘，即係06-07分就去到太子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n再下一班冇delay就06分到，石硤尾照常停站就10分到太子，即係太子嗰兩班車keep住隔3分鐘到站，叫做拉返勻個班次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b580427ccac17272888e8c3286a462d626b3641","tid":1809953,"uid":30751,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T13:04:27.000Z","msg":"唔好搭黨鐵好嗎"},{"pid":"4cfbf2d0b720781ca27097618d687af04d1a40c9","tid":1809953,"uid":123613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T13:08:30.000Z","msg":"話時話，鄰市2年前已經行緊呢套，為咗同黨接軌，黨鐵係時候要推行飛站常規班次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/452889/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/452889/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"730e56a469ee25ff050158e5e1d7c568578be8f9","tid":1809953,"uid":123613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T13:13:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"110cebfe0f782439d3202eaf202e80abd8fcc2e5","tid":1809953,"uid":141886,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T13:19:56.000Z","msg":"屌 去到今日仲搭mtr你不如死撚咗佢啦"},{"pid":"d7940ae6e3f4bf4dcfc2650685601dbe2c1ccb1d","tid":1809953,"uid":123613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"110cebfe0f782439d3202eaf202e80abd8fcc2e5","tid":1809953,"uid":141886,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T13:19:56.000Z","msg":"屌 去到今日仲搭mtr你不如死撚咗佢啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T13:24:20.000Z","msg":"我唔搭，仲有大把港豬搭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"563c63d6f70a9c9f4697f07b6f1ddd73f295e02c","tid":1809953,"uid":123613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T17:32:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}